{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Madness of the Science is set in 2060 in an advanced laboratory cut off from the outside world. In this dark and dangerous environment, an explosion causes artificial intelligences to degrade and living beings to mutate.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207800/extras/mosGif.gif?t=1729864928\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the main character Dr. Stephen Huxley, you and the Agent, the only robot in this world unaffected by the explosion, will try to stop these deadly threats in the lab. Your goal is to destroy the out-of-control robots and mutated creatures before they spread across the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207800/extras/mosAjan.gif?t=1729864928\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story-Based Gameplay: Delivering an FPS experience backed by an immersive story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique Ability Tree: Personalize your gameplay with unique abilities inspired by scientists of the past, different turret options and character development.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boss Sequences: Push your limits with exciting boss battles that require you to develop different strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intense Atmosphere: Experience moments of suspense in the dark corridors of the closed lab and use your wits to survive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">join Our Community</h2></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207800/extras/MOS_Discord.png?t=1729864928\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamst